McKenzie dropped by Symonds off S Lee on 11* with South Africa 54/1
South Africa 100 in 158 mins, off 222 balls
Gilchrist only the second player after Marsh to take 5 catches in an innings for Australia, the 19th player out of 27 occasions
Gilchrist set a new ODI world record of 6 catches by a wicket keeper
Australian 50 in 42 mins, off 62 balls including 8 fours
4th wicket partnership between Martyn and Bevan 50 in 30 mins off 48 balls

stories.title: Australia makes the most of flat South Africa
stories.summary: As you would expect from World Cup champions, Australia bounced off the ropes and stubbed out South Africa's aim of wrapping up the Challenge Series at Newlands last night and head for the Wanderers on Sunday mentally better prepared
